There are two sets of elevators from the garage - one to the hotel, the other to a condo building above the hotel.	You need your room key card to enter different section of the hotels,including to be able to operate the elevator.	Security was very good as you need to use your room card key to use the elevators and to enter the parking lot.	Security is better than in most hotels as guests need a room key card to operate the elevator.	You need your room key to activate the elevators, a security feature I like very much.	And the elevator access to/from the parking garage is a bit confusing and inconvenient.